data.message: Before the video was released , I used to listen Headlights and feel like bit weeping , I always tried in Youtube searching out the original , but there was none . Today when the Video released I just teared it out man ... This is damn heart touching video , This is would be a great Mothers Day for Em and for her Mom . Just love you Eminem , And the rumours are this was your last album . Please Em for our sake don't retire . We need you , Your songs gives a hope to our fuckin life :)
